		"description": {
			"value": "<p>You can use @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.9Y7fh4iRtGJkjixc]{Thirsting Weapon} three times per short rest, instead of just once.</p><p>Additionally, you gain the following feature:</p><p><strong>Once Per Turn</strong> - 1 Creature - Magical</p><ul><li><p>When you hit with a weapon attack, you deal an extra [[/damage 1d6]] force, necrotic, or psychic damage.</p></li><li><p>You can then choose to expend one of your hit dice to roll it and regain a number of hit points equal to the roll plus your charisma modifier.</p></li></ul>",
